fields.name: o_ProgramStartDt
fields.expression:
IIF (SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,3,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,6,1)='/', TO_DATE(ProgramStartDt, 'MM/DD/YYYY'),
 IIF (SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,2,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,5,1)='/', TO_DATE('0' || ProgramStartDt, 'MM/DD/YYYY'),
  IIF (SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,3,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,5,1)='/', TO_DATE(SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,1,3) || '0' || SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,4,6), 'MM/DD/YYYY'),
   IIF (SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,2,1)='/' AND SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,4,1)='/', TO_DATE('0' || SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,1,2) || '0' || SUBSTR(ProgramStartDt,3,6), 'MM/DD/YYYY'),NULL))))
